<ul>
<li>Prepare for mobile use</li>
<li>Simplify duplicate content</li>
<li>Switch off old servers and editing tools</li>
<li>Modernize appearance</li>
<li>Update old content</li>
</ul>
<p>Even though we have made changes, there are still many sites that need to be migrated to our new system. This is why web users are experiencing the old and new websites at the same time. We understand this might be confusing and frustrating, please realize that over 150 people are working to migrate content content on the old websites to the new system.</p>
